<div id="outline-container-sec-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Interesses de pesquisa (Research interests)</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">
<p>
Meus interesses de pesquisa incluem Hidrologia, Micrometeorologia, Turbulência
e Matemática Aplicada. Isso inclui as aplicações usuais em Engenharia e
Meteorologia, tais como estudos de Evaporação em Lagos, Modelos Chuva-Vazão,
Modelos de Qualidade do Ar, etc..
</p>

<p>
I work in Hydrology, Micrometeorology, Turbulence and Applied Math. This
includes applied studies in Engineering and Meteorology such as Lake
Evaporation, Rainfall-Runoof Models, Air Quality Models, etc..
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-2" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-2"><span class="section-number-2">2</span> Talks</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-2">
