You  may have a glimpse of my research by looking at some of my talks. Here is a sample.
</p>

<p>
See <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/ktkk9mqapvdfbhc/aphurst.pdf?dl=0">here</a>  my presentation at the VIII Brazilian Micrometeorology Workshop, Santa Maria, RS, Nov 11 2015.
